WEBVTT

00:01.068 --> 00:05.070
NARRATOR: It is a book
that caused a global sensation.

00:05.106 --> 00:07.973
WILLIAM SHATNER: A book
that says aliens visited Earth

00:08.074 --> 00:10.175
and then helped build
the pyramids

00:10.211 --> 00:11.977
influences the whole world.

00:12.079 --> 00:15.347
NARRATOR: It challenged
everything we thought we knew

00:15.383 --> 00:17.983
about humanity's past.

00:18.085 --> 00:18.984
<i>Mamma mia!</i>

00:19.086 --> 00:22.354
It 100% questioned

00:22.390 --> 00:26.492
orthodox ideas of archaeology.

00:26.594 --> 00:28.961
A lot of people
violently disagree with you...

00:29.063 --> 00:30.540
ERICH VON DANIKEN:
It's absolutely normal

00:30.564 --> 00:32.075
in our society
that I am attacked.

00:32.098 --> 00:34.066
NARRATOR:
But after five decades

00:34.101 --> 00:36.668
of scrutiny and investigation,

00:36.771 --> 00:40.973
how has Erich von Daniken's
controversial theory held up?

00:41.075 --> 00:43.442
MEGAN FOX: We've had people
that have worked at NASA

00:43.477 --> 00:46.011
go on the record saying
that of course they believe

00:46.113 --> 00:47.679
extraterrestrial life exists.

00:47.782 --> 00:50.015
NARRATOR:
Join the world's prominent

00:50.117 --> 00:51.683
ancient astronaut theorists...

00:51.786 --> 00:54.620
-Wow.
-...as they separate fact...

00:54.655 --> 00:57.022
NICK POPE:
Researchers have a whole arsenal

00:57.124 --> 00:58.590
of tools at their disposal.

00:58.626 --> 01:00.437
NARRATOR:
...from fiction...

01:00.461 --> 01:02.105
WILLIAM HENRY:
We've seen this new generation

01:02.129 --> 01:05.197
of ancient astronaut theorists
bringing new facts

01:05.299 --> 01:06.610
that were
previously unavailable.

01:06.634 --> 01:09.501
NARRATOR:
...and explore what has become

01:09.603 --> 01:11.537
a worldwide phenomenon.

01:11.639 --> 01:13.705
ANNOUNCER:
...Erich von Daniken.

01:13.808 --> 01:16.075
DAVID CHILDRESS:
At no time has there ever been

01:16.110 --> 01:20.012
such a big wave
of people believing

01:20.114 --> 01:21.180
in alien life.

01:21.282 --> 01:23.215
NARRATOR:
It's a special

01:23.317 --> 01:25.217
two-hour <i> Ancient Aliens</i> event.

01:25.319 --> 01:28.587
SHATNER: Von Daniken's theory
is mesmerizing,

01:28.622 --> 01:32.357
because nobody knows anything.

